name: I climbed on the back of a giant albatross
description:
This is an original embroidery pattern drawn by me and includes 2 pages, the first with a photo of the finished embroidery with colour suggestions and stitches, and the second page has the embroidery pattern

Please note that this is a listing for a digital PDF file only
There is no shipping fee

*The PDF pattern will be emailed to you within 24 hours of receipt of payment

 **PLEASE be sure to include your current email address!!

***You will need a PDF file reader to open and print your pattern. If you don’t already have a PDF reader, you can find a free download here: http://get.adobe.com/reader/
